Deputy Prime Minister bilong Singapore Wong Kan Seng i tok halo long em na em i toktok wantaim Prime Minister Lee Hsien Loong long 'trade' na 'terrorism'.
Maski i gat ol dispela kain toktok, Ma i win long wanpela 'platform' taim em i toktok long America i mas gat gutpela rilesensip wantaim China.

'National football' bilong Italy, wantaim 'national football' tim bilong Germany em tupela namba tu tim we i gutpela tru insait long olgeta hap bilong graun na ol i bin sempion bilong FIFA World Cup long 2006.

Long 10-pela yia, National Congress of Brazil i bin tok pait long mekim dispela i kamap olsem samting we lo i tok orait long en, na dispela kain marit aninit long lo em i orait long Rio Grande do Sul.
'Car camping' em i isi long mekim sapos yu gat wanpela bikpela 'minivan', SUV, Sedan o Station Wagon we i gat sit bilong putim go daun.
Bikpela Amazon River em i 6,387 km (3,980 miles). Em i save kolektim ol wara i kam long planti tausen liklik wara.

Ol narapela saintis i tok pait olsem dispela ol plent (plant) ol i pulap long poisin olsem na ol dainaso i no inap long kaikaim ol, maski long tude, ol 'sloth' na ol narapela animal olsem ol 'parrot' (wanpela tumbuna bilong ol dainaso) i ken kaikai ol lip o frut we i gat poisin long en.
Ol saintis i painim ol 'landform' we i stap long kainkain ples long antap long mun we ol i kolim olsem ol 'lobate scarps' na ol i kamap bikos mun i wok long slek isi isi tru.

MRI em i wanpela samting long sait bilong 'physics' we ol i kolim 'nuclear magnetic resonance' (NMR), we Felix Bloch na Edward Purcell i bin painimaut long 1930s taim (Felix i wok long Stanford University) na (Edward i wok long Havard University).
Armenia i sanap baksait long ol, na ol i kamap wantaim nupela 'republic'. Tasol, ol i no kamap olsem wanpela kantri ‑ Armenia tu ‑ i no luksave long ol olsem ol i wanpela kantri.

Ol dispela kainkain konstraksen (construction) i gat kainkain samting ol i ken mekim, sampela em ol i ken save long ol kainkain 'wave-length' na ol i gat ol kainkain level bilong strong bilong ol, na tu ol i nidim ol kainkain proses (process) long mekim mining long ol samting i kam insait long ai na ol i nidim ol kainkain namba bilong samting long wok gut.
Schumacher em i pinis long 2006 bihain long em i winim Formula 1 championship sevenpela taim, na ol i makim em long kisim ples bilong Felipe Massa bikos em i gat bagarap long bodi bilong em.

Taim em i wok olsem NSA, em i helpim Carter long mekim ol gutpela disisen long ol 'world affairs', kain olsem Camp David Accords, long 1978; na mekim rilesensip namel long US–China i kamap gut long 1970; Iranian Revolution, we i bin kamapim 'Iran hostage crises', long 1979; na taim Soviet i go insait long kantri Afghanistan, long 1979.
Dispela em i yu ken mekim wantaim wanpela nomol kar taim yu mekim gut plen, tasol i gutpela moa long yuim 4x4 kar na planti ol hap em yu ken go long en wantaim wanpela 'high wheel base' 4x4.
Long dispela taim em i stap wantaim dispela tim, em i skorim (score) 403-pela gol insait long 468-pela taim we em i pilai.
Ol lain i bin yusim ol 'submarine' long World War I na World War II. Long dispela taim ol i save ron isi isi tru na i no save sutim samting we i stap longwe long ol.
Sapos yu stap long wanpela siti we i gat kainkain kalsa bilong dring, go long ol 'bar', o 'pub' we stap klostu na yu no save go long em planti taim.
Wara em i narapela eksampel. Dispela kompaun (compound) i gat tupela 'hydrogen atom' na wanpela 'oxygen atom'.
Sapos yu no gat wanpela 'data connection' long fon bilong yu, o taim fon bilong yu i stap 'out of range', pefomens bilong em bai i no inap long wok gut o i no stap.
Eksampel em, “'learning” and “socialization'” em ol impoten motivesen (motivation) we i save mekim ol manmeri i laik long yusim intanet (James et al., 1995).

Sampela bilong ol 'cruise' i save tok olsem ol i karim ol lain i go long Berlin, Germany insait long ol 'brochure' bilong ol. Olsem yu ken lukim long mep (map) i stap antap Berlin i no stap klostu long solwara na wanpela visit long siti em i no stap insait long prais bilong 'cruise'.
Vidal i gat 28-pela krismas bin joinim Barça long tripela sisen (season) i go pinis, long Sevilla.
'Interactive design' em i nisim ol komponen (component) bilong wanpela projek long konek gut wantaim wanpela narapela, tasol ol i mas i gat mining taim ol i stap ol yet tu.
